    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/fe709a2490a0bc77380a3cc14a7fd6f7.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>历史之初，青铜时代的王们建立了最早的帝国。在这款独具风格的4X游戏中，为他们的崛起筹谋划略吧。扩展本国边界，在战略要地树立城池，然后组建起军队保卫你的领土。每个回合，你都要从数个机遇中选择一个，达成其目标来获得奖励。随机的取胜条件使得每场游戏都与众不同；可自定的取胜条件，探索各种各样的玩法！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/d5d0f582f72c03948637338159f21d6d.poster.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/d5d0f582f72c03948637338159f21d6d.webm?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/d5d0f582f72c03948637338159f21d6d.mp4?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/bff6adba6acf0877c74005c99d27dc50.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 专注战略，而非战术。普通4X游戏内繁琐的事都已被我们取其精华，去其糟粕。<br></li><li> 战斗被全新的战力系统所简化，没有复杂的回合制战斗，只需要合理分配军队和舰队的位置以及移动就可。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/65b5e9bdb8c6a7ac9fed39c7c6eaedad.poster.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/65b5e9bdb8c6a7ac9fed39c7c6eaedad.webm?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/65b5e9bdb8c6a7ac9fed39c7c6eaedad.mp4?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/9294af2096cdee342b9f26965d15eb17.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 八张手工制作的地图，包含了青铜时代的世界各地，深度体验不同地域带来的机遇与困难。<br></li><li> 52个可玩的帝国，每个都有自己的特点，可以按自己的喜欢去挑选并迎接独特的挑战！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/01dceba37ee5abe14286834fed6a9d77.poster.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/01dceba37ee5abe14286834fed6a9d77.webm?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/01dceba37ee5abe14286834fed6a9d77.mp4?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/5d8ec635fc7b01b2dc044c5f5fd84ae2.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 通过参与著名探险家格特鲁德·贝尔的短篇故事，了解游戏的基础知识。<br></li><li> 与我们的大数据人工智能做对抗，它们不会作弊，公平竞争。试着战胜它！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/e2d35a5cb98e038c3a88da9b58c68f60.poster.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/e2d35a5cb98e038c3a88da9b58c68f60.webm?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/e2d35a5cb98e038c3a88da9b58c68f60.mp4?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/1bdfbc11bb1353b033d7d62552edd17f.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 多人联机，同时操作，不用等待。大家的每一步都尽在眼底。<br></li><li> 在 ‘实时’（短暂回合计时）或‘异步’（较长游戏计时）两种计时模式中，一鸣惊人，赢得宝藏！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/11fa180e8f92978e8cead6e2ea6ac0e8.poster.avif?t=1729044948\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/11fa180e8f92978e8cead6e2ea6ac0e8.webm?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768280/extras/11fa180e8f92978e8cead6e2ea6ac0e8.mp4?t=1729044948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
